						               													<description>From the box:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This magnetic game with colour-changing pieces puts your logic and memory to test!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The special SATA pieces each contain four different colours. Depending on which space and orientation they are placed in on the SATA board, a different colour will be displayed in the window. The object of the game is to make a &amp;ldquo;triad&amp;rdquo; &amp;ndash; a straight line of three SATA pieces in a row that show the same colour in their windows. This is not as easy as it sounds, since each time you move or twist a piece, its colour changes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Learning to play SATA is very simple &amp;ndash; but to become a SATA Master you will need to learn the patterns behind the colour changes. SATA is a captivating logic game for everyone aged 7+!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Contents: SATA board with 3 score markers, 8 SATA pieces and rules.&amp;#10;The pieces are stored in the flip-down sides of the board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
